    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/1365bbe7b74e15aa566ea0f14aaaecb1.avif?t=1753525025\" width=616 height=113 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/bee1630d158fd9cb948f60f2860d9f36.poster.avif?t=1753525025\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/bee1630d158fd9cb948f60f2860d9f36.webm?t=1753525025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/bee1630d158fd9cb948f60f2860d9f36.mp4?t=1753525025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A rogue-lite where you must find the exit while mowing down thousands of enemies, leveling up and selecting your gear.<br>Entering a dungeon, your mission is to explore, unlock characters and equipment and escape using one of the exits.<br>After each run you use the loot to buy equipment, upgrade weapons, pay artisans to craft or hire adventurers for the next run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/709c2f67608b51f6882cd72374766d9a.avif?t=1753525025\" width=616 height=113 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/5dc34f038fa42431f32580930446497b.poster.avif?t=1753525025\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/5dc34f038fa42431f32580930446497b.webm?t=1753525025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/5dc34f038fa42431f32580930446497b.mp4?t=1753525025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play co-op (1 - 5 players) or solo<br></li><li>Unlock more weapons, armor and artifacts<br></li><li>Unlock more characters, some by defeating them<br></li><li>Fight mini bosses for exit keys<br></li><li>Find hidden items and discover how they work<br></li><li>Find secret exits that unlock more maps</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/ad6f55926ab6c34df7e93e30cc1409c3.avif?t=1753525025\" width=616 height=113 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/6d36453acf85723d25b4b9ce395c2129.poster.avif?t=1753525025\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/6d36453acf85723d25b4b9ce395c2129.webm?t=1753525025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220870/extras/6d36453acf85723d25b4b9ce395c2129.mp4?t=1753525025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock your main weapons for all characters to use<br></li><li>Escape alive to earn bonus gold<br></li><li>You can choose the order of levelling your weapons' stats<br></li><li>Once you've levelled all your equipment, you will get gold, food, or the option to drop some<br></li><li>Chests contain more unlocks so keep an eye open for them on the mini map<br></li><li>Armor comes in sets that have a matching artifact<br></li><li>To fuse armor with it's artifact, you simply max the artifact's level and it will free up a slot<br></li><li>Find the exit key in chests or from mini bosses<br></li><li>Find your secondary weapon in a gold chest<br></li><li>Unlock map-specific weapons, making them available in your loadouts<br></li><li>Weapon status effects can harmonize or cancel out, so choose them carefully</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Latest Updates</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hatch pets from monster eggs<br></li><li>Mine crystals and use gem cutting to produce marbles<br></li><li>Enhance weapon damage using 6 types of crystal marbles<br></li><li>Use followers and helpers to harvest and fight for you<br></li><li>Set up Loadouts to limit the equipment you find during play<br></li><li>Use artisans to craft potions, weapons, artifacts and even playable characters</li></ul>",
